author: Zapp_Brannigan
title: Not as good as the others
review: This set has a realistic design, but the front suspension should be real, not pipes. For this reason, the set has a rating of 3/5. Other details include rear suspension, one piston engine, and a gear system with chains. Overall good price but the set isn't as good.
